title: GARNET MAGIC HILLS
detail: The Villa is part of Developed gated community at Garnet Hills offering spacious 3 BHK and 4 BHK  Bungalows. Enjoying  host of top-notch amenities, perfect for every family. Located in the scenic Ambivali village, close to major shopping, entertainment, schools, and hospitals
city_description: Find peace & quiet in Khalapur. Enjoy breathtaking views and fresh air, yet stay connected to Mumbai & Navi Mumbai. Ideal for weekend getaways or a permanent retreat. Be part of a growing community with convenient access to amenities. This scenic location offers both tranquility and investment potential.
